al price premiums.","summary":"India plans 1.5M ton sugar export quota due to higher domestic surplus, benefiting producers like Shree Renuka, Balrampur Chini, EID Parry.\nIndia's sugar output for 2025-26 is estimated at 30.95M tons, with exports likely facing challenges due to local price premiums.","url":"https://in.marketscreener.com/news/india-plans-1-5-mln-ton-sugar-export-quota-on-higher-domestic-surplus-ce7d5fdbde8cfe2d","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-11-10T00:00:00","source":"MarketScreener India"},{"id":"352726","title":"Shree Renuka Sugars approved unaudited financial results for Q2 and H1 FY25, reporting consolidated revenue of ₹42,889 Mn.\nBoard approved conversion of ₹573.65 Mn loan to KBK Chem Engineering into equity, aiming to strengthen capital structure and reduce debt.","summary":"Shree Renuka Sugars approved unaudited financial results for Q2 and H1 FY25, reporting consolidated revenue of ₹42,889 Mn.\nBoard approved conversion of ₹573.65 Mn loan to KBK Chem Engineering into equity, aiming to strengthen capital structure and reduce debt.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=fe6b61b4-72a1-4976-beb4-5b5256076603.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-11-06T19:06:54","source":"BSE"},{"id":"774264517795023104","title":"Shree Renuka Sugars reports Q2 loss of ₹3,495 Mn and H1 loss of ₹6,423 Mn.\nCompany's net worth is negative ₹9,262 Mn as of Sep 30, 2025.","summary":"Shree Renuka Sugars reports Q2 loss of ₹3,495 Mn and H1 loss of ₹6,423 Mn.\nCompany's net worth is negative ₹9,262 Mn as of Sep 30, 2025.","url":"https://sqst.in/6d05P","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-11-06T19:00:46","source":"ScoutQuest"}]}]